174 A.3d 504 STRUCTURED ASSETS TRUST, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. RANDALL R. LONG, DEFENDANT, AND CHARLOTTE F. LEWIS, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-140 September Term 2017

079329 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000164-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
